Colfax Products and Services Colfax Fluid Handling has built the business on strong products and services‚ those that lead the industry with specific pump technologies and fluid handling solutions. While Allweiler‚ COT-Puritech, Houttuin‚ Imo‚ LSC‚ Rosscor‚ and Warren represent a full-spectrum of diverse pump products and deep expertise in critical and demanding applications‚ they share a single-minded focus on and commitment to customers. Colfax's strategic market leaders and their teams leverage these brands to develop and deliver customized solutions‚ backed by experienced service and support‚ that meet the specific needs of customers around the world.


