Colfax  creates solutions that make the world work. Our companies lead their respective industries in providing critical equipment and innovative capabilities. Colfax Fluid Handling  offers a broad range of precision pumps and systems, backed by industry expertise and outstanding global service. ESAB  provides excellence in welding and cutting solutions for manufacturing, fabrication and maintenance applications across a broad spectrum of industries. Howden  offers a broad range of precision rotating equipment and systems and application expertise in specific industries, backed by outstanding global service.






